<paragraph blockId="22.[151,1058,783,835]" pageId="22" pageNumber="981">
E t y m o l o g y: The trivial name, 
<emphasis box="[568,643,783,804]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="981">acicula</emphasis>
, is a Latin noun with a meaning of &quot;needle&quot;; with reference to the acuminate phallic apex.
</paragraph>
